article.description: — Justice Hill hit eight 3-pointers and finished with 36 points — both career highs — and Murray State beat Belmont 82-60 Saturday night.
article.headline: Hill hits 8 3s to help Murray St. beat Belmont 82-60
article.linkText: Hill hits 8 3s to help Murray St. beat Belmont 82-60
article.story: NASHVILLE, Tenn. -- — Justice Hill hit eight 3-pointers and finished with 36 points — both career highs — and Murray State beat Belmont 82-60 Saturday night. Tevin Brown added 18 points and KJ Williams 13 for Murray State (14-2, 4-0 Ohio Valley Conference). Ben Sheppard scored 13 points, Nick Muszynski added 12 and Luke Smith 11 for Belmont (13-4, 3-1). ------
